## What good looks like

### Expected output
- Script starts and prints the chapter banner.
- Core pipeline phases are visible in logs.
- Final section prints a concise result object/text.

### Common failure cases
- Missing `OPENAI_API_KEY`
- Corporate SSL interception (`AGENTIC_DISABLE_SSL=1`)
- Optional dependency not installed

